    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>More recently, refers to roads over which mail is carried. Historically, roads with stations providing for horses for postriders, mailcoaches, or travelers. More recently, refers to roads over which mail is carried. Historically, roads with stations providing for horses for postriders, mailcoaches, or travelers.</Note_Text>
